title: Brand New, Luxury VanMission Studios!
map_address: 42 Otis St near S Van Ness Ave
posting_body: ['**4 Weeks Free for 12 months+ Lease!!', 'Applied to end of lease term**', 'Brand new, luxury studios at 42 Otis now available for rent!', 'Just steps from Hayes Valley & Civic Center, located in the up & coming VanMission neighborhood.', 'This new construction, luxury studio unit is conveniently located within walking distances to central Hayes Valley, Theatre District, and Mission District.', '42 Otis has a 97 Walk Score/ 99 Transit Score.', 'Home features include: open floor plan, sleek designer kitchen with Bertazzoni appliances, StudioBecker cabinetry, air conditioning/ heating, in-home w/d, elevator, and secure bike parking, as well as secure package lockers.', 'Please message us if you are interested.', 'Serious renters only.', 'For a private tour of the building, appointments are available M-F 8AM-6PM and Saturday 9AM-12PM.', '*Please note:', '- Units starting at $2,650/mo.', 'Unit 501 pictured is for $2,800/mo.', '- Renters have the option to have your unit to come furnished!', '- Flexible lease terms', '- **4 Weeks Free for 12 months+ Lease!!', 'Applied to end of lease term**', 'Also for additional monthly, can furnish units.']
